title: House for RENT - One Bedroom House in Los Angeles
posting_body: ['Hidden gem!', 'This well maintained house is centrally located in East Los Angeles and close to many amenities.', 'Looking for responsible and clean tenant/s. Max occupancy, 2 people.', 'This 1 bedroom/1 bath recently renovated house (back house - separate unit) is located on a quiet residential street with its own separate yard, privacy fence and across the street from a church.', 'Location provides you with close proximity to public parks, K-12 schools, grocery stores, gas stations, restaurants, bakeries, and access to 5/10/60/710 freeways.', 'House is close to several key locations including:', '* Downtown Los Angeles (DTLA, 7 miles)', '* California State University, Los Angeles (Cal State LA, 2 miles)', '* East Los Angeles College (ELAC, 2 miles)', 'Included:', 'House is furnished with refrigerator and gas stove', 'Water is also included', 'Washer/Dryer hook-up available', '***Please note***', 'NO pets allowed,', 'NO exceptions', 'NO smoking', 'NO subletting']
